ze=xsmall&avatarId=10232","24x24":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?size=small&avatarId=10232","32x32":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?size=medium&avatarId=10232","48x48":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?avatarId=10232"},"displayName":"Olivier Lamy","active":true},"body":"Rename to Registry.","updateAuthor":{"self":"http://jira.codehaus.org/rest/api/2/user?username=olamy","name":"olamy","emailAddress":"olamy@apache.org","avatarUrls":{"16x16":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&avatarId=10232","24x24":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?size=small&avatarId=10232","32x32":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?size=medium&avatarId=10232","48x48":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?avatarId=10232"},"displayName":"Olivier Lamy","active":true},"created":"2007-02-07T16:46:58.637-0600","updated":"2007-02-07T16:46:58.637-0600"},{"self":"http://jira.codehaus.org/rest/api/2/issue/47096/comment/87050","id":"87050","author":{"self":"http://jira.codehaus.org/rest/api/2/user?username=brettporter","name":"brettporter","emailAddress":"brett@apache.org","avatarUrls":{"16x16":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&avatarId=10232","24x24":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?size=small&avatarId=10232","32x32":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?size=medium&avatarId=10232","48x48":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?avatarId=10232"},"displayName":"Brett Porter","active":true},"body":"see the plexus-registry module. More could surely be added...","updateAuthor":{"self":"http://jira.codehaus.org/rest/api/2/user?username=brettporter","name":"brettporter","emailAddress":"brett@apache.org","avatarUrls":{"16x16":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&avatarId=10232","24x24":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?size=small&avatarId=10232","32x32":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?size=medium&avatarId=10232","48x48":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?avatarId=10232"},"displayName":"Brett Porter","active":true},"created":"2007-02-07T22:00:55.872-0600","updated":"2007-02-07T22:00:55.872-0600"},{"self":"http://jira.codehaus.org/rest/api/2/issue/47096/comment/87093","id":"87093","author":{"self":"http://jira.codehaus.org/rest/api/2/user?username=olamy","name":"olamy","emailAddress":"olamy@apache.org","avatarUrls":{"16x16":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&avatarId=10232","24x24":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?size=small&avatarId=10232","32x32":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?size=medium&avatarId=10232","48x48":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?avatarId=10232"},"displayName":"Olivier Lamy","active":true},"body":"Transform plexus-registry with the following structure :\r\n- plexus-registry-api\r\n- plexus-registry-test\r\n- plexus-registry-naming\r\n- plexus-registry-commons (plexus-registry-commons-configuration is a liitle ugly :-) \r\n\r\nNote for the last one system properties are added by default (field addingSystemProperties)\r\n\r\nMade work all test in (system properties override with c-c).\r\nThis needs to be implemented with naming ?\r\nNot sure of this :  adding comment on method Registry getSubRegistry( String key ); (throws NoSuchElementException if not found).\r\n\r\nNot yet implemented in naming :\r\n- addConfigurationFromFile\r\n- addConfigurationFromResource\r\n- dump()\r\nIn a next patch ;-)\r\n\r\nIn fact we could change to \r\n{noformat} \r\nplexus-registry-api\r\nplexus-registry-test\r\nplexus-registry-providers \r\n  plexus-registry-naming\r\n  plexus-registry-commons\r\n{noformat}\r\n\r\n--\r\nOlivier\r\n","updateAuthor":{"self":"http://jira.codehaus.org/rest/api/2/user?username=olamy","name":"olamy","emailAddress":"olamy@apache.org","avatarUrls":{"16x16":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&avatarId=10232","24x24":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?size=small&avatarId=10232","32x32":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?size=medium&avatarId=10232","48x48":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?avatarId=10232"},"displayName":"Olivier Lamy","active":true},"created":"2007-02-08T10:43:45.706-0600","updated":"2007-02-08T10:43:45.706-0600"},{"self":"http://jira.codehaus.org/rest/api/2/issue/47096/comment/87146","id":"87146","author":{"self":"http://jira.codehaus.org/rest/api/2/user?username=brettporter","name":"brettporter","emailAddress":"brett@apache.org","avatarUrls":{"16x16":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&avatarId=10232","24x24":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?size=small&avatarId=10232","32x32":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?size=medium&avatarId=10232","48x48":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?avatarId=10232"},"displayName":"Brett Porter","active":true},"body":"I think the last suggestion is best. It's a bit hard for me to tell what is changed in your patch vs. moved (and there are a number of formatting changes as well). I'm going to continue with work here today as is (not a lot of changes to the registry expected), and have put you up for commit so hopefully you can rearrange things yourself, then make the enhancements to tests you've proposed.\r\n\r\nI don't think Naming needs to be backed by system properties.\r\n\r\nI'm going to revise the way I dealt with sub registries - this was simply to make it possible to get the modello plugin working while I got some other things in place. The current technique certainly won't work with naming unless we follow the (0) notation in lists...","updateAuthor":{"self":"http://jira.codehaus.org/rest/api/2/user?username=brettporter","name":"brettporter","emailAddress":"brett@apache.org","avatarUrls":{"16x16":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&avatarId=10232","24x24":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?size=small&avatarId=10232","32x32":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?size=medium&avatarId=10232","48x48":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?avatarId=10232"},"displayName":"Brett Porter","active":true},"created":"2007-02-08T17:23:30.848-0600","updated":"2007-02-08T17:23:30.848-0600"},{"self":"http://jira.codehaus.org/rest/api/2/issue/47096/comment/87621","id":"87621","author":{"self":"http://jira.codehaus.org/rest/api/2/user?username=olamy","name":"olamy","emailAddress":"olamy@apache.org","avatarUrls":{"16x16":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&avatarId=10232","24x24":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?size=small&avatarId=10232","32x32":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?size=medium&avatarId=10232","48x48":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?avatarId=10232"},"displayName":"Olivier Lamy","active":true},"body":"committed in rev [5696|http://fisheye.codehaus.org/changelog/plexus/?cs=5696]\r\nThe groupId has been changed to org.codehaus.plexus.registry.","updateAuthor":{"self":"http://jira.codehaus.org/rest/api/2/user?username=olamy","name":"olamy","emailAddress":"olamy@apache.org","avatarUrls":{"16x16":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&avatarId=10232","24x24":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?size=small&avatarId=10232","32x32":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?size=medium&avatarId=10232","48x48":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?avatarId=10232"},"displayName":"Olivier Lamy","active":true},"created":"2007-02-14T15:24:09.957-0600","updated":"2007-02-14T15:24:09.957-0600"},{"self":"http://jira.codehaus.org/rest/api/2/issue/47096/comment/87640","id":"87640","author":{"self":"http://jira.codehaus.org/rest/api/2/user?username=trygvis","name":"trygvis","emailAddress":"trygvis@inamo.no","avatarUrls":{"16x16":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&avatarId=10232","24x24":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?size=small&avatarId=10232","32x32":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?size=medium&avatarId=10232","48x48":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?avatarId=10232"},"displayName":"Trygve Laugstøl","active":true},"body":"I think the group id should remain org.codehaus.plexus unless you have ideas to turn this into something bigger, like a sub-project of Plexus.","updateAuthor":{"self":"http://jira.codehaus.org/rest/api/2/user?username=trygvis","name":"trygvis","emailAddress":"trygvis@inamo.no","avatarUrls":{"16x16":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&avatarId=10232","24x24":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?size=small&avatarId=10232","32x32":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?size=medium&avatarId=10232","48x48":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?avatarId=10232"},"displayName":"Trygve Laugstøl","active":true},"created":"2007-02-15T02:02:49.357-0600","updated":"2007-02-15T02:02:49.357-0600"},{"self":"http://jira.codehaus.org/rest/api/2/issue/47096/comment/87642","id":"87642","author":{"self":"http://jira.codehaus.org/rest/api/2/user?username=olamy","name":"olamy","emailAddress":"olamy@apache.org","avatarUrls":{"16x16":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&avatarId=10232","24x24":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?size=small&avatarId=10232","32x32":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?size=medium&avatarId=10232","48x48":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?avatarId=10232"},"displayName":"Olivier Lamy","active":true},"body":"Is there any issue concerning the groupId naming (I don't know some introspection or something somewhere) ?\r\nIMHO, I think we can use a sub groupId of org.codehaus.plexus for component which a complicated structure with sub modules.\r\nWith this the browse of the [repo|http://repo1.maven.org/maven2/org/codehaus/plexus/] could be more easily redeable with a sub one.\r\nI think  about :\r\n- logging\r\n- mail \r\n\r\nNote the component plexus-cache (in sandbox) use a similar groupId org.codehaus.plexus.cache.\r\n\r\nI think it's more easily readable for users.\r\nLook on snapshot repo \r\n- [registry|http://snapshots.repository.codehaus.org/org/codehaus/plexus/registry/]\r\n- [cache|http://snapshots.repository.codehaus.org/org/codehaus/plexus/cache]\r\n\r\nWDYT ?\r\n\r\n","updateAuthor":{"self":"http://jira.codehaus.org/rest/api/2/user?username=olamy","name":"olamy","emailAddress":"olamy@apache.org","avatarUrls":{"16x16":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&avatarId=10232","24x24":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?size=small&avatarId=10232","32x32":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?size=medium&avatarId=10232","48x48":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?avatarId=10232"},"displayName":"Olivier Lamy","active":true},"created":"2007-02-15T02:21:53.303-0600","updated":"2007-02-15T02:21:53.303-0600"}]},"timeoriginalestimate":null,"aggregatetimespent":null}}